headline : Meron Estefanos - a refugee activist
text : \r\nMeron Estefanos is an activist and radio journalist originally from Eritrea, but she now lives in Sweden. She has been fighting for the rights of kidnapped refugees for years, sometimes also negotiating their release. She helps the families of those kidnapped to stay informed about their status. She has been raising international awareness of the plight of those trying to flee from Eritrea.\r\n
